item.title: Prometheus Heavy Industries
item.description: PHI Or Prometheus Heavy Industries has recently acquisitioned several companies such as Slater Group, Slater Heavy Industries and Hammerhead Armaments. This along with several property purchases puts PHI As the number 1 arms and machinery manufacture in San Andrenas Located at Maze bank tower (west) on prosperity. Purchase News PHI Acquires Slater Group, Slater Heavy Industries, RRI And Hammerhead armaments Jan 2023 Prometheus Heavy Industries proudly announces the acquisition of Slater Group, Slater Heavy Industries, RRI And Hammerhead armaments.
